558
00:42:18,510 --> 00:42:26,100
Where our promise shines brightly

559
00:42:27,270 --> 00:42:32,440
Try! Comforting words are like a breeze

560
00:42:32,690 --> 00:42:36,740
That don't reach my heart

561
00:42:36,740 --> 00:42:45,160
The anxieties I shoulder, grow

562
00:42:46,000 --> 00:42:50,380
But I make my own decisions

563
00:42:50,380 --> 00:42:54,590
So, I will probably be alright on my own

564
00:42:55,130 --> 00:43:00,050
Even if I stumble, even if I get lost

565
00:43:00,050 --> 00:43:04,430
There is always tomorrow

